    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to exacting standards. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, featuring an immaculate exterior and a pristine interior that reflects a rigorous preservation history. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. We invite you to experience the pinnacle of its class with this peerless offering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
